1.Make a github repo
2.cd HackBulgaria
3.git init
4.git add. #vsichki failove v papkite ili add file.py
5.git commit -m "Add first file" #or some other name
6.git remote add origin https:// ....
7.git pull origin master
8.git push origin master

Adding file
1. creating file
2. git add name of file
3. git commit -m "Adding file"
4. git push origin master

Delete file
1. git rm name of file
2. git commit -m "Deleting file"
3. git push origin master

Always when you commit something u have to push it inside GitHub
git status checking the status of our git